        <h1 class="cw-h1">IxTheo Account</h1>
        <p>If you create a personal account, additional functions are available to you. You only need to register once with a valid email address, a username and a password; further details are optional. Registration is free of charge.</p>   
        <p>The link for registration and login is located at the top right corner and is labelled "login".</p>
        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0px;"><img src="/themes/ixtheo2/images/content_img/en/login_button_eng.png" style="width: 80%;" alt="<?=$this->transEscAttr('symbolic_image_table58');?>" /></p>
        <p>After you log in, the "My Account" button is displayed near the place where the “Login” button was. Click on it to access the following functions in your account:</p>
