                        <p>To create a list, select the function "Create a List" on the right-hand side under "My Lists". You can freely choose the title and description of your list. The "Access" option underneath the description field allows you, when you create the list or modify it later, to decide whether the list should be viewed only by you (setting: "Private") or whether you would like to share it with other users (setting: "Public").</p>

