                        <p>To share public lists with other people, simply copy the list URL from your browser and send it as a link. <a target="_blank" href="https://www.ixtheo.de/MyResearch/MyList/83">Example of a public list with literature suggestions on the topic "Christianity and Europe"</a></p>
                        <p>Whenever you save new publication entries, you can choose in which list you would like to keep them. You can find all lists under the menu item "My Lists".</p>

